<p>
	Weekend / evening work will be involved so flexibility is a must. We are ambitious and keen to give exceptional people more responsibility. We are offering a competitive salary which will be based on your level of experience and value we think you will bring to the business. This is a full-time role based in Clerkenwell, London.</p>
